# 🏥 Hospital Management System (C++)

## Overview
A beginner-friendly **Hospital Management System** developed in **C++** using **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)** and a **Singly Linked List**. This console application helps manage patient records through a menu-driven interface.

## Features
- Add a new patient
- Display all patients
- Search patient by ID
- Update patient details
- Delete a patient
- Count total patients
- Exit the application

## Concepts Used
- Classes and Objects
- Encapsulation
- Constructors
- Singly Linked List
- Dynamic Memory Allocation
- Functions
- Loops and Conditional Statements


## Menu
```
1. Add Patient
2. Display Patients
3. Search Patient
4. Update Patient
5. Delete Patient
6. Count Patients
7. Exit
```

